# 💬 Quotes App  

A simple and elegant web app that displays random inspirational quotes. Built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** to motivate users with new quotes every time they visit or click refresh.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🎯 Fetches random quotes from an API (or local JSON)
- 🎨 Clean and responsive design
- 🌙 Light/Dark mode toggle
- 🗣️ Text-to-Speech feature
- 📋 Copy quote to clipboard
- 💖 Save favorite quotes in localStorage
- 📱 Works on mobile and desktop

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript  
- **API:** [https://api.quotable.io/random](https://api.quotable.io/random)  
- **Hosting:** GitHub Pages / Netlify  

---

## ⚙️ Installation & Usage

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/arpittak027/Quotes-app.git

# Go into the folder
cd Quotes-app

# Open index.html in your browser
````

Or just visit: 👉 [Live Demo (if hosted link available)](https://arpittak027.github.io/Quotes-app)

